 <metadata>
  <name>RTR - Outwood OAB</name>
  <desc>This route goes the full length of the Outwood trail. For those wanting to do a longer run you can do the whole trail (and back, obviously!) everyone else will run for 20 minutes down the trail and then turn around and come back.</desc>
